folder: Flatbush Avenue & Tillary Street, Brooklyn, NY
text:
Flatbush Avenue Extension, north from Tillary Street. The view is from Tillary and Bridge Streets, across the trianguler plot which separates Bridge Street (left) from Flatbush Avenue Ext. The tall building is the Brooklyn Technical high School.

August 23, 1939

P. L: Eperr

folder: Tillary St. & Flatbush Ave., Brooklyn, NY
text:
Tillary Street, east from Flatbush Avenue Extension. This view is of the south side of Tillary Street across Flatbush Avenue Extension, after the north side was cleared of all its buildings in connection with the proposed construction of Fort Greene Houses.

August 23, 1939
P. L. Sperr
